risk_assessment = assessment.risk_assessment
risk_objects = assessment.risk_objects
risk_metadata = assessment.meta_data
risk_properties = assessment.risk_objects_properties
reference_data = assessment.reference_data
assessment.draw_risk_object_values(risk_type='physical', property_name='Data Risk', title='Physical Objects by Risk Score')
assessment.draw_risk_object_values(risk_type='virtual', property_name='Risk Score', title='Virtual Objects by Risk Score')
assessment.draw_risk_object_values(property_name='Total Risk', title='All Objects by Risk Score')
assessment.draw_risk_object_values(risk_type='physical', property_name='Total Risk', title='Physical Objects by Total Risk')
assessment.draw_risk_object_values(risk_type='virtual', property_name='Total Risk', title='Virtual Objects by Total Risk')
assessment.draw_risk_object_values(risk_type='physical', property_name='Control_Adequacy', title='Physical Objects by Conrtol Adequacy')
assessment.draw_risk_object_values(risk_type='virtual', property_name='Control_Adequacy', title='Virtual Objects by Conrtol Adequacy')
assessment.draw_risk_object_connections_basic(risk_type='physical', title='Number of connections "child only" for physical risks', connection_type='child')
assessment.draw_risk_object_connections_basic(risk_type='virtual', title='Number of connections "child only" for virtual risks', connection_type='child')

# Risk Object connections count (child connections)
assessment.draw_risk_object_connections_basic(title='Number of connections "child only" for all risks', connection_type='child', 
                                              riskID_mode=False)
assessment.draw_risk_object_connections_basic(risk_type='physical', title='Number of connections "parent only" for physical risks', connection_type='parent')
assessment.draw_risk_object_connections_basic(risk_type='virtual', title='Number of connections "parent only" for virtual risks', connection_type='parent')
assessment.draw_risk_object_connections_basic(title='Number of connections "parent only" for all risks', connection_type='parent')
assessment.draw_risk_object_connections_basic(risk_type='physical', title='Number of connections for physical risks')
assessment.draw_risk_object_connections_basic(risk_type='virtual', title='Number of connections for virtual risks')
assessment.draw_risk_object_connections_basic(title='Number of connections for all risks', riskID_mode=False)
